data.description: Impeccably Renovated & Breathtaking - The perfect blend of elegance, comfort & convenience. This immaculate 2 bdrm., 1.5 bath Condo is luxuriously renovated from floor to ceiling with high-end upgrades throughout. Enter the spacious living room & set the mood with impressive recessed ceiling lighting. Show off the Custom Kitchen with sparkling Granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, wall-to-wall Custom Kitchen cabinets & absolutely beautiful large Granite topped Island with extra storage.  The King sized private Master bedroom suite has been updated to include ceiling lighting & beautiful upscale flooring - it also boasts a renovated bath & huge, brightly lit walk-in closet. The 2nd bedroom is also unusually large in size - upgraded ceiling lighting & huge french door closet add character. Both bedrooms face the lovely, private, well manicured courtyard, which is available for your enjoyment. Paying further attention to detail - the windows tilt inward for easy cleaning, remote controlled energy efficient in wall air conditioners, renovation of the main bath includes an exhaust fan for your comfort. Enjoy your beautiful private balcony for breakfast in the morning or romantic sunset evenings. Enjoy low, low common charges with includes, heat, water, security patrol, maintenance of the grounds, private children's play area & more.  Community Room is available for private events & off street parking is available for only $55 additional monthly.   Centrally located near all - shopping, restaurants, public transportation, religious & cultural Institutions, Shirley Chisholm State Park, Belt Parkway - easily accessible to any of the 5 boroughs, LI & NJ.  Mint condition. Nothing to do - just move in.  Seller wants to hear all offers.
